I'm sorry, but we didn't call you.

1535
01:34:34,168 --> 01:34:35,252
Are you okay?

1536
01:34:53,979 --> 01:34:56,774
My baby died.

1537
01:34:57,608 --> 01:34:58,484
I know.

1538
