1576
01:40:57,176 --> 01:41:01,554
<i>Soft, strong, a fragile life</i>

1577
01:41:01,555 --> 01:41:07,144
<i>That keeps the world from ending, yeah</i>

1578
01:41:10,105 --> 01:41:13,608
